Pow! / Disney Deal | POW! Entertainment




















































Pow! / Disney Deal
Symbol : POWN



 
POW! had a “first look” agreement with Silver Creek Pictures, Inc., an affiliate of the Walt Disney Company (“Disney”) for the term of five years which ended in December 2014.  The agreement called for POW! to provide Silver Creek Pictures with a “first look” at all of POW!’s creative intellectual property and the right to acquire any such properties at Silver Creek Picture’s discretion.












