POW! Entertainment Inc.


            
            POW! Entertainment, Inc. operates as a multimedia production and licensing company. It creates, develops and licenses intellectual properties for traditional entertainment media, including: feature length films in live action and animation, television programming, merchandising and related ancillary markets. The company was founded by Stanley Martin Lieber, Gill Champion, and Arthur M. Lieberman on August 17, 1998 and is headquartered in Beverly Hills, CA.

            
            (See Full Profile)


  



 


